cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with network slicing and resource allocation in a multi-UAV-aided network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves optimization of network resources and energy efficiency, which are related to information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the control of network resources and power consumption of UAVs, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves optimization problems, which are related to artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with enhanced mobile broadband (eMBB) service, which involves multimedia content delivery.
